(161, 'Memory Plus, USA', '0', '0', 12332, 'product-featured-161.jpeg', '<p><b>Memory Plus</b> is a dietary supplement that combines nutrients essential for a healthy nervous system and brain. Vitamins B1, B6 and B12 are essential for the nervous system. They are involved in cognitive and learning activities, mental health and the protection of nerve endings.</p><p><b><u>Memory Plus benefits:</u></b></p><p><b>Folic Acid</b> is required for energy production and is involved in the normal process of cell development.</p><p><b>Mineral calcium</b> provides energy and participates in the construction of proteins related to genetic processes. It is necessary for proper cognitive performance and psychological well-being.</p><p><b>Ginkgo Biloba</b> is a plant extract that has been used for centuries to support the health of the cardiovascular system.</p><p><b>Glutamic Acid</b> is an amino acid that performs neurotransmitter function. It is important for the potassium transport and metabolism of fat and sugar.</p><p><b>Choline Bitartrate</b> is associated with the vitamin B complex. It is related to the cell membrane functions and the production of a neurotransmitter involved in memory activity and control of muscles.</p><p><b><u>Features of Memory Plus:</u></b>\r\n<br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"></p><ul><li> Provides essential nutrients for the health of the brain and nervous system</li><li> Promotes a healthy cardiovascular system</li><li> Helps the good performance of the cognitive activity and psychological well-being</li><li> Made in the<b> USA</b></li></ul><p><b>Directions: </b>Serving per container 60 tabs. </p><p><b>Adults:</b> Take one (1) tablet one to two times daily as a diet supplement, preferable with a meal.</p><p><b>Cautions: </b>Store tightly closed in a dry place at a controlled temperature of 59º-86º F.</p><p>Do not use it if the safety seal is broken or missing. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p> <b>Size:</b> 60 or 100 capsules.</p>', '', '', '