(165, 'Collagen Pro-X Shampoo', '0', '0', 4635, 'product-featured-165.jpg', '<p>Collagen Pro-x Hair Shampoo, 250ML a Uniquely formulated Collagen, Biotin & Caffeine infused with Rosemary essential oil. Collagen Pro-X has developed a new pharmaceutical grade formulation shampoo, which has a unique combination of natural Marine Collagen, infused with Biotin, Caffeine and Rosemary essential oil to make your hair thicker and fuller. The growth cycle of hair consists of three phases; First the Growth phase; in which hair grows to its full length, Second the Regression phase; in which the hair stops growing, Third the Rest phase; during which hair is forced out by the growth of the new hair. A daily hair wash with Collagen Pro-X shampoo, enhances the blood circulation to the scalp and promotes optimum nutrition of the hair follicles during the phases of hair growth. Thus, the activity of the ingredients in Collagen Pro-X shampoo will stimulate hair growth at the roots and reduce hair loss, making your hair stronger, thicker and fuller.</p><p><br></p><p><b>Ingredients:</b></p><p><br></p><p>Collagen, Biotin & Caffeine infused with Rosemary essential oil.</p><p><b>Made in Britain</b>, GMP Quality, Halal Certified.</p>', '', '', '', '', 9, 1, 1, 3),
